  "title": "SENIOR QUANTITY SURVEYOR",
  "description": "<p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Must have Bachelor's Degree in Civil Engineering, Quantity Surveying, Construction Management or related qualifications</li><li>Minimum 10 years of relevant experience in the construction industry.</li><li>Excellent time management skills, with ability to work to tight deadlines.</li></ul><p>Job Description:</p><ul><li>Reviews tender documents / requests for proposal to understand project details and requirements.</li><li>Supporting in quantity take offs, estimation, prepare tender submission, cost planning, sourcing sub-contractors, forecast budgeting, variation orders, final accounts</li><li>Preparation of list of prequalified bidders for comparison, cost analysis, negotiations and awarding of sub-contractors· Preparation of tender submissions, when required</li><li>Liaise with suppliers and contractors to get proposals/quotations and carry out evaluation</li><li>Preparation and Issuance of Contracts to Sub-Contractors and Suppliers</li><li>Reviewing of tender documents, drawings, and requirements</li><li>Prepare and analyse costings for tender</li><li>Getting involved in post-tender submission activities</li></ul>",
